    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438165286&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606208122/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438165286&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1065\" data-width=\"1894\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"625541181\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606208122\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"563247dc-7007-4d2d-ae6b-ab8194375265\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438165286&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=854 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/MetallicWorkflow_Banner.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438165286&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=427 1x\"></span><p>Whether you’re using PBR maps from an online material library or texturing software like Substance Painter.  RenderMan ships with a handy node called <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224201\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMetallicWorkflow</a>, which can be easily used with your PBR maps and a Lama workflow.</p><p>This lesson will guide you through the process.</p><p>The maps used in this lesson were kindly provided by our rendering friends at <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://greyscalegorilla.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Greyscalegorilla</a>, and the example used is Copper Corroded Heavy 01</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760439230819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606208122/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760439230819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"636\" data-width=\"1280\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"625508453\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606208122\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"4c7ded8b-2685-4e31-b86a-fcd2356274ca\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760439230819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1280&amp;height=636 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/GSG_CorrodedCopper.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760439230819&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=377 1x\"></span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"1c6b0834-8aef-4e6e-8bf9-253e034f8cfc\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>As the Eagle model doesn’t have any UVs, we’re using a triplanar approach to mapping the textures onto the model via the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542224293\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrMultiTexture </a>node</p><p>If your model has UVs, you can use a <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542225070\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrTexture </a>node instead of the PxrMultiTexture node.</p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_MatellicWorkflow.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/Lama_MatellicWorkflow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438153889&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=332\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/606208122/Lama_MatellicWorkflow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438153889&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"985\" data-width=\"2249\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"625508440\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_MatellicWorkflow.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"606208122\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"2546376a-3cd3-4d6d-a1da-f37dc36f9674\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/Lama_MatellicWorkflow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438153889&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=664 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/606208122/Lama_MatellicWorkflow.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760438153889&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=332 1x\"></span><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;border-color: #998DD9;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #EAE6FF;\">\n<p>Note: Currently, exporting a Lama material network from Substance Painter requires updating the normal connections.  You can easily do this by selecting Update Lama Nodes from the RenderMan menu in your DCC</p>\n</div></div>"
    }
